39500	BEIJING , Sept. 4 -lrb- Xinhua -rrb-
39501	there be `` quality problem '' with some school building damage during the catastrophic earthquake in southwest China 's Sichuan Province on May 12 , a official say here on Thursday .
39502	the problem could have happen because some school room be build too fast without regard to quality in recent year , Ma Zongjin , director of the the National Wenchuan Earthquake Expert Committee , say at a press briefing on the evaluation of the earthquake aftermath .
39503	it be fear the death toll in the 8.0-magnitude earthquake center in Wenchuan County , Sichuan , will top 87,000 .
39504	many victim be student kill in collapsed building .
39505	this have arouse wide suspicion and anger over shoddy construction and substandard material allegedly use to build school .
39506	the chinese government have also promise to investigate the issue .
39507	various factor might work jointly to damage thousand of school building in the earthquake area , such as the intensity of the quake , and poor design , Ma say .
39508	for example , if the roof of a classroom be too wide , it will be too weak to withstand strong quake , he say .
39509	Prof. Shi Peijun with the committee say among 845.1 billion yuan -lrb- about 121 billion U.S. dollar -rrb- in direct economic loss for the May 12 earthquake , 20.4 percent come from damage essential public building such as school and hospital .
39510	Ma say the Ministry of Construction send more than 2,000 expert to area affect by the earthquake to investigate .
39511	`` the earthquake be so powerful and destructive in some area that not only school building , but office and residential building be all damage , '' he say .
39512	but poor design by architect and the use of substandard building material might also have play a role in the massive destruction , he say .
39513	`` it be possible there be problem with those building , because there have be a rush of construction of school recently , '' he say .
39514	Ma say the investigation would provide guideline for reconstruction of school and hospital in future .
795372	HAVANA , Feb. 24 -lrb- Xinhua -rrb-
795373	cuban army general Raul Castro be elect president of Cuba Sunday to replace he brother Fidel Castro , during a legislative session at Cuba 's palace of convention in the capital Havana .
795374	Raul Castro be bear on June 3 , 1931 in Cuba 's Oriente Province and educate at Jesuit school and the University of Havana .
795375	he be the younger brother of Fidel Castro Ruz , Cuba 's leader from 1959 until 2006 .
795376	in 1953 he take part with Fidel in the attack on the Moncada barracks -- a attempt to oust the authoritarian regime of Fulgencio Batista .
795377	he be sentence to 13 year ' imprisonment after the insurrection fail , but pardon in 1955 .
795378	he join he brother 's movement in Mexico and return to Cuba in December 1956 and participate in the successful 1959 revolution .
795379	Raul have serve as the chief of Cuba 's armed force since February 1959 .
795380	he be deputy prime minister from 1972 to 1976 .
795381	and when Cuba reform its system of governance in 1976 he become the first vice-president of the Council of State , the nation 's cabinet , whose president be leader of the nation .
795382	he be continuously elect as the first vice-president of the Council of State in 1981 , 1986 , 1993 , 1998 and 2003 .
795383	lawmaker give Raul a standing ovation at the start of Sunday 's session of the nation 's legislature , the National People 's power assembly , which meet to choose the nation 's 31-member council of state .
795384	Raul have head Cuba 's caretaker government for 19 month , since Fidel Castro announce he have undergo a emergency intestinal surgery and be provisionally cede power in July 2006 .
795385	Raul be marry to fellow revolutionary Vilma Espin from 1959 until she death in June 2007 .
795386	the couple have four child .
795387	Raul be say to be a doting father and a enthusiastic climber .
795798	Havana , Feb. 24 -lrb- Xinhua -rrb- -- Raul Castro be elect on Sunday as president of Cuba to replace he brother Fidel Castro .
