1291629	meanwhile , of the top 10 importer during the year , the Myanmar Petrochemical Enterprise rank the first with 676.3 million dollar , the MOGE the second with 150.8 million dollar , follow by Myawaddy Trading -lrb- 91.2 million dollar -rrb- , Myanmar Railways -lrb- 54 million dollar -rrb- , Rothmans -lrb- 40 million dollar -rrb- , Electric Power Enterprise -lrb- 36.9 million dollar -rrb- , Cooperative export and import enterprise -lrb- 30.6 million dollar -rrb- , Myanmar Posts and Telecommunications -lrb- 27 million dollar -rrb- , Department of Health -lrb- 20 .
1291630	9 million dollar -rrb- and the United State Embassy -lrb- 20.7 million dollar -rrb- for import goods relate to the construction of its new compound in Yangon .
1291631	accord to the report , Myanmar obtain 7.93 billion dollar in its foreign trade in 2006-07 , up 43 percent over the previous year with surplus of 2.09 billion dollar , attribute to the government 's `` export first , import second '' strategy .
