1502574	if the Malays want to correct the situation , it be not because of my quit .
1502575	if they be brave to save the party and the party 's struggle , they must be brave to act , '' he say .
1502576	Mahathir reiterate that Badawi must relinquish he prime minister 's post to ensure UMNO 's survival and if necessary , UMNO member can pass a vote of no confidence to force Badawi to step down .
1502577	ask whether he latest move to quit the UMNO be to apply pressure on Abdullah , Dr Mahathir say : `` I do not know about pressure because this man do not seem to understand anything . ''
