2028895	the economic downturn and inflation in Taiwan have definitely play a role in the change , and that be why my company have see steady growth in the number of student go to study English in Cebu , Kao say .
2028896	as of June , JLEC have send 60 student to Cebu , double the number during the same period last year , with 80-90 percent of they repeat client who have opt for longer course from two month to six month instead of two to four week .
2028897	another factor that make Cebu more appealing to those who would like to learn English be that they can start course every Monday , while tradition study tour be confine to set period of time and require a minimum number of student to be hold , Kao say .
2028898	also , both CELI and CPILS have business english program suitable for those who would like to improve they english proficiency on job , Kao say .
2028899	he think all the factor mention above make Cebu a more attractive english - learn destination than western country .
