2988645	Reagan want more time to strengthen the fragile lebanese government , but McCain worry that the american force be too small and that U.S. interest do not justify the risk .
2988646	in a similar vein , when Saddam Hussein invade Kuwait in 1990 , McCain initially want to limit the response to a air war .
