2988650	he write later that he regret the step as a encroachment on the president 's power and `` as a retreat in the face of aggression from a inferior foe . ''
2988651	McCain oppose the U.S. military intervention in Haiti in 1993 .
2988652	like then-president Clinton , he be reluctant to intervene in Bosnia in 1993 and 1994 .
