23563331	smaller business in Massachusetts would pay lower tax , but large out-of-state company with operation in the Bay State would pay more under change to the state 's tax code move through Beacon Hill , revenue specialist say .
23563332	the House of Representatives last week approve Governor Deval Patrick 's proposal to change the way Massachusetts calculate business tax liability , particularly for those company that have operation in multiple location .
23563333	currently corporation pay tax only on the income earn by they Massachusetts unit .
23563334	this method have spawn a industry of tax scheme for company to minimize liability by divide profit and loss strategically among various unit .
23563335	the new mechanism would use what be know as `` combined reporting , '' in which a company 's profit be tax accord to a formulum that consider its sale , payroll , and capital asset in the state .
