23563339	the Patrick administration estimate a change to combined reporting would raise a additional $ 188 million in revenue next year .
23563340	but opponent say that with the economy slowing , now be a bad time for any tax increase on large company that sustain huge number of job .
23563341	`` I can not define a exact group who will be impact , but what I do know be the weight of this will fall most heavily on large , multistate corporation that employ hundred of thousand of Massachusetts citizen , '' say Michael Widmer , president of the Massachusetts Taxpayers Foundation , a nonprofit business advocacy group .
